public interface InterleavedParallelRoutingFlow
extends StructuredFlow

A StructuredFlow which contains a set of activities which must be performed according to a predefined set of partial orderings. Partial orderings are defined using a collection of Activity arrays. Each array [A1, A2, ... An] defines precedence relations; thus A1 must be executed before A2, A2 before A3, and so on.
If all the activities are presential, meets the Interleaved Parallel Routing pattern (WFP17).
